Product: AmazonBasics Double-Door Folding Metal Dog Crate - Medium (36x23x25 Inches)
Review_Summary: I am very pleased with the dog crate. Very sturdy. No damage or flaws. Was better than some others that I have purchased in a retail store.

Product: AmazonBasics Double-Door Folding Metal Dog Crate - Medium (36x23x25 Inches)
Review_Summary: The price of the item was very good compared to other cages however the item itself came tilted so now my dog has a tilted dog crate. The tilt to the gates are noticeable but not very drastic. For the price I'll live with it.
